hadiths[40]{hadithnumber,text}:
1080,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka mein fateh Makka ke mauqe par) unnees din thahrey aur barabar qasr kartey rahe. isliye unnees din ke safar mein ham bhi qasr kartey rahtey hain aur us se agar zyada ho jaey to poori Namaz padhtey hain.
1081,ham Makka ke irade se Madina se nikley to barabar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2-2 rakaat padhtey rahe. yahan tak ke ham Madina wapas aaey. maine puchha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka Makka mein kuchh din qiyam bhi raha tha? to uska jawab Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye diya ke das din tak ham wahan thahrey they.
1082,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Mina mein 2 rakaat (yani char rakaat wali namazon mein) qasr padhi. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi unke daure-khilaafat ke shuru mein 2 hi rakaat padhi thin. lekin baad mein aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne poori padhi thin.
1083,aap ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein amn ki haalat mein hamein 2 rakaat Namaz padhai thi.
1084,"maine Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed se suna, wo kehtey they ke hamein Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mina mein char rakaat Namaz padhai thi lekin jab iska zikr Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se kya gaya to unhon-ne kaha ke (انا لله و انا اليه راجعون). phir kehney lagey maine to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina mein 2 rakaat Namaz padhi hai aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi maine 2 rakaat hi padhi hain aur umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi 2 rakaat hi padhi thi kash! mere hisse mein un char rakaton ke bajaey 2 maqbool rakatein hotiin."
1085,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba ko sath lekar talbiya kehtey huey Zil-Hijja ki chothi taareekh ko (Makka mein) tashrif laey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jinke paas qurbani ka janwar nahi hai wo bajaey Haj ke Umra ki niyat kar lein aur Umra se farigh ho kar halal ho jayen phir Haj ka ehram baandhein. is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ata ne Jaabir se ki hai.
1086,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye farman naql kya tha ke auratein teen din ka safar kisi mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ke baghair na karein (abu-Usaama ne kaha haan).
1087,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aurat teen din ka safar us waqt tak na karey jab tak iske sath koi mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) rishtedar na ho. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ahmed ne ibne-Mubarak se ki unse Ubaidullah Umri ne unse Naafe ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se.
1088,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi khatun ke liye jo Allah aur uske rasool par eman rakhti ho, jaaiz nahi ke aik din raat ka safar baghair kisi zi raham mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ke kare. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir , Suhel aur Malik ne Maqbari se ki. wo is riwayat ko Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they."
1089,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina Munawra mein Zohar ki char rakaat padhi aur zul-Hulaifa mein Asr ki 2 rakaat padhi.
1090,pahley Namaz 2 rakaat farz hui thi baad main safar ki Namaz to apni usi haalat par reh gaee albatta hazar ki Namaz poori (chaar rakaat ( kar di gaee. Zohri ne bayan kya ke maine Urwa se puchha ke phir khud Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kyon Namaz poori padhi thi unhon-ne iska jawab ye diya ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski jo taaweel ki thi wahi unhon-ne bhi ki.
1091,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha jab safar mein chalney ki jaldi hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib ki Namaz der se padhtey yahan tak ke maghrib aur isha aik sath mila kar padhtey. Salim ne kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi jab safar mein jaldi hoti to is tarah kartey.
1092,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne maghrib ki Namaz us din der mein padhi thi jab unhein unki biwi Safiya-binte-abii Ubaid ki sakht bimari ki itlaa mili thi (chaltey huey) maine kaha ke namaaz! (yani waqt khatm hua chahta hai) lekin aap ne farmaya ke chaley chalo phir dobara maine kaha ke Namaz ! aap ne phir farmaya ke chaley chalo is tarah jab ham 2 ya teen meel nikal gaey to aap utrey aur Namaz padhi phir farmaya ke maine khud dekha hai ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein tezi ke sath chalnaa chahtey to isi tarah kartey they Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi farmaya ke maine khud dekha ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (manzile-maqsood tak) jaldi pahunchnaa chahtey to pahley maghrib ki takbeer kahalwaatey aur aap uski teen rakaat padha kar salam phertey. phir thodi der thahar kar isha padhatey aur uski 2 hi rakaat par salam phertey. isha ke farz ke baad aap sunnatein wghaira nahi padhtey they aadhi raat ke baad khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey.
1093,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke ontni par Namaz padhtey rahtey chahe iska munh kisi taraf ho.
1094,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nafl Namaz apni ontni par ghair qible ki taraf munh karke bhi padhtey they.
1095,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) nafl Namaz sawari par padhtey they. isi tarah witr bhii. aur farmatey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi aisa kartey they.
1096,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) safar main apni ontni par Namaz padhtey chahe iska munh kisi taraf hota. aap isharon se Namaz padhtey . aap ka bayan tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi isi tarah kartey they.
1097,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ontni par Namaz nafl padhtey dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar ke isharon se padh rahe they iska khayal kiye baghair ke sawari ka munh kidhar hota hai lekin farz namazon mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah nahi kartey they.
1098,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) safar mein raat ke waqt apne janwar par Namaz padhtey kuchh parwah na kartey ke iska munh kis taraf hai. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi ontni par nafl Namaz padha kartey chahey iska munh kidhar hi ho aur witr bhi sawari par padh letey they albatta farz is par nahi padhtey they.
1099,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ontni par mashriq ki taraf munh kiye huey Namaz padhtey they aur jab farz padhtey to sawari se utar jatey aur phir qible ki taraf rukh karke padhtey .
1100,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) se jab ( Hajjaj ki khaleefa se shikayat karke) wapas huey to ham unse Ainut-Tamar mein miley. maine dekha ke aap gadhey par Sawar hokar Namaz padh rahe they aur aap ka munh qible se baain taraf tha. is par maine kaha ke maine aapko qible ke siwa dusri taraf munh karke Namaz padhtey huey dekha hai. unhon-ne jawab diya ke agar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisa kartey na dekhta to main bhi na karta. is riwayat ko Ibrahim ibne- tahmaan ne bhi Hajjaj se, unhon-ne Anas bin Sirin se, unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya hai."
1101,maine safar mein sunnaton ke mutaalliq Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha aap ne farmaya ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein raha hun. maine aapko safar mein kabhi sunnatein padhtey nahi dekha aur Allah ka irshad hai ke tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai.
1102,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein raha hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein 2 rakaat (farz) se zyada nahi padha kartey they abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisa hi kartey they."
1103,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unhon-ne chasht ki Namaz padhtey dekha haan Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke fateh Makka ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke ghar ghusl kya tha aur uske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aath (8) rakatein padhi thin, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi itni halki phulkii Namaz padhtey nahi dekha albatta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo aur sajda poori tarah kartey they."
1104,"unhon-ne khud dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (raat mein) safar mein nafl namazein sawari par padhtey they, wo jidhar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ley jati udhar hi sahii."
1105,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ontni ki peeth par chahe iska munh kisi taraf hota nafl Namaz sar ke isharon se padhtey they. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi isi tarah kya kartey they.
1106,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko agar safar mein jald chalnaa manzoor hota to maghrib aur isha aik sath mila kar padhtey.
1107,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein Zohar aur Asr ki Namaz aik sath mila kar padhtey, isi tarah maghrib aur isha ki bhi aik sath mila kar padhtey they."
1108,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein maghrib aur isha aik sath mila kar padhtey they. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ali bin-Mubarak aur Harab ne Yahya se ki hai. Yahyaa, Hafs se aur Hafs Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (maghrib aur ishaa) aik sath mila kar padhi thin."
1109,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab jaldi safar tay karna hota to maghrib ki Namaz me deri kar detey. phir usey isha ke sath mila kar padhtey they. Salim ne bayan kya ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi agar safar tezi ke sath tay karna chahtey to isi tarah kartey they. maghrib ki takbeer pahley kahi jati aur aap teen rakaat maghrib ki Namaz padh kar salam pher detey. phir maamooli se thehraaw ke baad isha ki takbeer kahi jati aur aap uski 2 rakatein padh kar salam pher detey. donon namazon ke darmyan aik rakaat bhi sunnat wghaira na padhtey aur isi tarah isha ke baad bhi Namaz nahi padhtey they. yahan tak ke raat ke beech mein aap uthtey (aur tahajjud ada kartey).
1110,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un 2 namazon yani maghrib aur isha ko safar mein aik sath mila kar padha kartey they.
1111,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) agar suraj dhalney se pahley safar shuru kartey to Zohar ki namaze-Asr tak na padhtey phir Zohar aur Asr aik sath padhtey aur agar suraj dhal chuka hota to pahley Zohar padh letey phir sawar hotey.
1112,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab suraj dhalney se pahley safar shuru kartey to Zohar Asr ka waqt aaney tak na padhtey. phir kahin (raastey mein) thahartey aur Zohar aur Asr mila kar padhtey lekin agar safar shuru karne se pahley suraj dhal chuka hota to pahley Zohar padhtey phir sawar hotey.
1113,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar they isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ghar mein baith kar Namaz padhai, kuchh log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey khadey ho kar padhney lagey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ishara kya ke baith jao. Namaz se farigh honey ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey isliye jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo aur jab wo sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthaao."
1114,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey se gir padey aur uski wjah se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain pahlu par zakhm aa gaey. ham haal-chaal poochhney ke liye gaey to Namaz ka waqt aa gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baith kar Namaz padhai. ham ne bhi baith kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi mauqe par farmaya tha ke imam isliye hai taake uski pairwi ki jaey. isliye jab wo takbeer kahey to tum bhi takbeer kaho, jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo, jab wo sar uthaey to tum bhi sar uthao aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( ربنا ولك الحمد ( kaho."
1115,"aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha (doosri sanad) aur hamein Ishaq-bin-Mansur ne khabar di, kaha ke hamein Abdus-Samad ne khabar di, kaha ke maine apne bap Abdul-Waris se suna, kaha ke ham se Husain ne bayan kya aur unse ibne-bareeda ne kaha ke mujh se Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, wo bawaaseer ke mareez they unhon-ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi aadmi ke baith kar Namaz padhney ke barey mein puchha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke afzal yahi hai ke khadey ho kar padhey kyonke baith kar padhney waley ko khadey ho kar padhney waley se aadha sawab milta hai aur letey-letey padhney waley ko baith kar padhney waley se aadha sawab milta hai."
1116,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baith kar Namaz padhney ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khadey ho kar Namaz padhna afzal hai lekin agar koi baith kar Namaz padhey to khadey ho kar padhney waley se usey aadha sawab milega aur let kar padhney waley ko baith kar padhney waley se aadha sawab milega. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( farmatey hain ke hadis ke alfaz main ( نائم ( ) مضطجع (ke mana mein hai yani let kar Namaz padhney wala.
1117,mujhey bawaaseer ka marz tha. isliye maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz ke barey mein malum kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khadey ho kar Namaz padha karo agar uski bhi taqat na ho to baith kar aur agar uski bhi na ho to pahlu ke bal let kar padh lo.
1118,"aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi baith kar Namaz padhtey nahi dekha albatta jab aap zaeef ho gaey to Quran ki qir'at namaaz mein baith kar kartey they, phir jab rukoo ka waqt aata to khadey ho jatey aur phir taqriban tees ya chalis (40) aayatein padh kar rukoo kartey."
1119,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tahajjud ki Namaz baith kar padhna chahtey to qirat baith kar kartey. jab taqriban tees chalis (40) aayatein padhni baqi reh jaatiin to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein khadey ho kar padhtey. phir rukoo aur sajda kartey phir dusri rakaat mein bhi isi tarah kartey. Namaz se farigh honey par dekhtey ke main jaag rahi hun to mujh se baatein kartey lekin agar main soti hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi let jatey.
